casebody.data:
No. 108,

Orig.

Nebraska v. Wyoming et al. [For earlier decision herein, see, e. g., ante, p. 40.]

Final motion of the Special Master for compensation and reimbursement of expenses granted, and the Special Master is awarded a total of $297,888.18 to be paid as follows: 42% each by Nebraska and Wyoming, 10% by the United States, and 6% by Basin Electric Power Cooperative.
